Title: Irresistible
Plot: A mortuary worker who gets his thrills from collecting hair and fingernails from the dead begins killing his soon-to-be collectibles himself and sets his seriously disturbed sights on Scully.
GuestStars: Nick Chinlund, Robert Thurston, Bruce Weitz, Christine Willes, Deanna Milligan, Glynis Davies, Tim Progosh, Dwight McFee, Maggie O'Hara, Mark Saunders, Clara Hunter, Denalda Williams, Kathleen Duborg
